# ggplotpy session protocol

## Start
1. Read `STATUS.md`, last `project_memory/progress_log.md` block, `blockers.md`.
2. State milestone, task ID, files to touch, verification tier(s).
3. Run `pytest tests/unit -q` when tests exist.

## End
1. Run task-appropriate tiers (T0 min; render→T1; aes/to_r→T2).
2. Append session block to `progress_log.md`.
3. Update `STATUS.md`; log pytest commands + pass/fail.
4. New decisions → `decisions.md`; gotchas → `discoveries.md`.

Use `project_memory/resume_prompts.md` #1 for general resume.
